title: Guns n Roses - Not in Miami's Lifetime (Live 3CD) 2017 ak320
description:
Guns n Roses - Not in Miami's Lifetime (Live 3CD) 2017 ak320

Guns N’ Roses:2017-08-08-Marlins Park, Miami, FL, USA 

Throughout the Not in This Lifetime reunion tour, Guns N' Roses have been peppering their nearly three-hour performances with some well-chosen covers. Axl Rose is fond of weaving in the Who's "The Seeker" into the encore and teasing Derek and the Dominos' "Layla" during "November Rain,". 

Slash and second guitarist Richard Fortus have been tag teaming Pink Floyd's "Wish You Were Here." Soundgarden's "Black Hole Sun" has now become a set staple following the death of Chris Cornell in May. They keep it up and Ill be making another Covers album from em.
